            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              中国以旧换新销售额突破1万亿人民币
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;relative min-w-[120px] w-[120px]&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img alt=&quot;中国以旧换新销售额突破1万亿人民币&quot; title=&quot;中国以旧换新销售额突破1万亿人民币&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/66657e2e7c5bc8ebf2e70eb60860dfa418dd4f6eaa56bb6edc24051ed807ff70&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
